6a92ed7","tid":668573,"uid":80140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2c6446a10e88c6fd2072d96852e49f06320fb1c","tid":668573,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8001c3f2994cc9770661ef1d14f2ceb5e87bd23","tid":668573,"uid":130950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54e9028b597adb37cf66714cb28b147e3f511e4d","tid":668573,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"係日本，D濕疹好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"上次秋天去日本 爆到比香港嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"日本乾，長期住先有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"不過呢個病好睇地區<br />\n我有個呀sir去左美國就好返曬 本來係香港好勁 十年都有<br />\n我女朋友一出世就有 不過去過兩次加拿大玩一兩個星期<br />\n果排都比香港好<br />\n一返香港落機果日即起 勁痕"},{"pid":"8cbb31e35f6ebd877718fd12d60a5c0c79c5581f","tid":668573,"uid":91922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T08:07:26.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都無, 呢幾年斷續有, 近呢一年越黎越嚴重<br />\n<br />\n睇西醫開藥膏食完搽完會好, 但過一陣就又黎過<br />\n<br />\n4個月前食左浸大果隻中藥喜膚靈, 食左兩個月後好左7成, 之後食多半樽食, 上星期轉左食中大果隻濕敏清, 食左一星期未見成效, 而且好貴<br />\n<br />\n以前試過好多方法, 保濕日日做, 注意衛生, 沖涼液小心揀<br />\nSO FAR 浸大果隻藥最幫到手, 中大果隻我唔敢肯定, 食多一排先知"},{"pid":"3d5ab380e92d3c726311368bfc888d27daf871f2","tid":668573,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"係，d印仲係到，啡啡地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68939fe7943bb569d2ddfe2bf0fb7e178c197011","tid":668573,"uid":140643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54e9028b597adb37cf66714cb28b147e3f511e4d","tid":668573,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T17:23:31.000Z","msg":"係日本，D濕疹好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"上年去左一個月，身上好勁多<br />\n但就到面瘋狂敏感，乾又衰唔乾又衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d968388e37d848c304c257c30fe3c82ebe205b7","tid":668573,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"今年好咗，咁熱都係得左手同心口少少加拿大兩邊摺位<br />\n唔知關唔關近一個月開始保持做運動嘅關係<br />\n不過未到七八月最熱唔知會點<br />\n上年就兩邊手心口背脊頸腳都有紅晒<br />\n又痕又痛瞓唔到，好撚慘"},{"pid":"079e9c339b5074816c689ff2d1d0fd9d7a356ab2","tid":668573,"uid":4929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:56:50.000Z","msg":"唉，求神拜佛唔好落咁多雨丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家都腳踝位，著襪都煩⋯⋯"}]}